label: AB2_tP3_123_a_h-001
title: Linzhiite (High Temperature FeSi$_2$) Structure
comments: This is the high temperature structure of FeSi$_{2}$.  The actual composition is Fe$_{x}$Si$_{2}$ with $x < 1$, and the transition temperature varies with composition between 962 and 1000K. (Villars, 2018) The low temperature structure is \href{current_web_home_dir/AB2_oC48_64_df_2g-001}{body-centered orthorhombic}.
